node_modules
dist
*.local
.DS_Store
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json

# Accumulated fetch output lives on the `data` branch now, not `main` — see
# CLAUDE.md's "Data lives on its own branch" section. Untracked here
# 2026-07-20 specifically so the nightly/every-3h fetch job never has
# anything to commit to `main` again; a human never needs to `git pull`
# before pushing just because the bot ran. The files still exist on disk
# after `npm run fetch-data` — git just stops caring about them here.
public/data/*.json
